skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: resistor colors
des:
Tell Resistor Colors what colors are on the resistor and alexa will return the value of that resistor in Ohms. Super helpful when your hands are full or you are busy assembling a project. 

Please note this does not use the tolerance band.
